{"tid":2020711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★攬炒Effect？】無需睇樓！新屯門中心近700萬元成交　創紀錄新高","createTime":"2020-05-17T09:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T05:15:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a20c14b9bb5d80c371a6aeef640db684b4325c2","tid":2020711,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"二手樓繼續破頂。置安居蘇永耀表示，屯門新屯門中心1座高層H室，實用面積597方呎。原業主因疫情關係，不開門睇樓。有睇樓已達3個月的買家，因鍾情單位全海景，無樓睇以屋苑歷來新高價698萬港元購入，呎價11,692元。據了解，屋苑對上紀錄為2018年錄得，當時做價695萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200517/bkn-20200517145403930-0517_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200517%2Fbkn-20200517145403930-0517_00842_001.html&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e615Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=93796285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200517/bkn-20200517145403930-0517_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f77122f419815c060f761eb81c510faf6148566f","tid":2020711,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e63ff5b5d818fb6b4b0647b507231d562be3b2e","tid":2020711,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"香港越攬炒 越好住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509917170f0452b1720f27710c8472b4aa720006","tid":2020711,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":